Package hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend.collections.impl Description

As a subpackage of hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend, provides backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution. Is not part of the public API.

To be specific, this package contains default implementations of the interfaces defined in the hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend.collections package.
